  "texts": [
    "Models were evaluated on the test set which maintained the real-world disease distribution. 4.",
    "The process was repeated for a total of three times using different random seeds for sampling.",
    "The results were then averaged.",
    "This is in line with similar experiments in previous research (Li et al., 2022) For the second experiment, the following steps were followed:",
    "The train and transfer learn datasets were recombined and a new train dataset was created with all patients from the state of Maryland excluded."
